OL,3,C'Dine and dash' - Three women rack up
OL,4,C#300 food bill and leave without paying
OL,6,FAn Italian restaurant in Sussex has
OL,7,Fbeen targeted by people dining and
OL,8,Fdashing, three times since October.
OL,10,FLa Bella Vista in St Leonards on Sea
OL,11,Fhas lost more than #1,000 in trade
OL,12,Fafter customers ordered food and left
OL,13,Fwithout paying.
OL,15,FAldo Esposito, who owns the
OL,16,Frestaurant, has now installed 16 CCTV
OL,17,Fcameras in a effort to stop any more
OL,18,Fincidents taking place.
