OL,4,C#300 food bill and leave without paying
OL,6,FIn one incident, caught on CCTV, three
OL,7,Fwomen leave the restaurant after
OL,8,Fracking up a bill of more than #300,
OL,9,Fone of them is seen coming back to
OL,10,Ftake her drink.
OL,12,FAldo Esposito said: "I feel
OL,13,Fdisappointed and frustrated with the
OL,14,Fsituation because we put a lot of love
OL,15,Fand effort into the business and
OL,16,Fdealing with situations like this is
OL,17,Fvery disheartening.
