OL,6,FLa Bella Vista was featured on ITV
OL,7,FMeridian in January after previously
OL,8,Fbeing victim to dine and dash
OL,9,Fcriminals.
OL,11,FCafe Number 35 in Canterbury also fell
OL,12,Fvictim to this type of crime, when a
OL,13,Fman and two children left without
OL,14,Fpaying for their breakfasts and drinks.
OL,16,FKate Nicholls, Hospitality UK said:
OL,17,F"This is crime, this is fraud, it's
OL,18,Fexactly the same as shoplifting and
OL,19,Fthe impact on the businesses is
OL,20,Fhuge... and we are seeing incidents
OL,21,Fincrease.
