OL,9,Feven. A quarter of them have no cash
OL,10,Freserves.
OL,12,F"This is taking much-needed cash from
OL,13,Fthose businesses. It's not a
OL,14,Fvictimless crime.
OL,16,F"For many it will be the final nail in
OL,17,Fthe coffin which could mean the loss
OL,18,Fof that business because it is
